{"tid":1908418,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人不能忘本！日本自民黨議員：容我稱之為「武漢肺炎」","createTime":"2020-03-03T09:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T11:24:06.000Z","uid":25468,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eb49a09ee0b8eb46efbc163c99a6f7fa2dd9e28e","tid":1908418,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/374/5e5e0a2a6c26b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F374%2F5e5e0a2a6c26b.jpg&h=382b2b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續延燒，針對疾病名稱，中國官方深怕沒有達到「去中國化」、「去武漢化」的效果，日前曾對此透過官媒批台灣政府大搞地域標籤，然而，在疫情日漸向世界各國延燒後，日本自民黨參議員山田宏在今(3)日參議院預算委員會當中表示，新型冠狀病毒會讓人忘記這病的起源在哪，因此容許他稱之為武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情爆發後，國際媒體一開始以「Wuhan pneumonia」、「Wuhan coronavirus」等用語稱之，使得中國官方在一月底及二月初不斷針對疾病名稱喊話，包含《環球時報》、《新華社》在內等多家中國官媒更於2月中旬接力狂批台灣，為武漢肺炎名稱出來「洗地」，文中大批台灣無視相關國際組織準則，對疫情大貼地域標籤。並強調「2019-nCoV」是疫情爆發之初，世衛組織給引發新冠肺炎病毒的暫時稱呼。現在世衛組織對新冠肺炎疾病的國際正式名稱則是「COVID-19」。前者是病毒名，後者是疾病名。<br />\n<br />\n半個月後過去，在今日的日本參議院預算委員會當中，<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">日本自民黨參議員山田宏表示，「新型冠狀病毒發源自中國武漢，容許我稱其為武漢肺炎」，他直言，新型冠狀病毒會讓人忘記這病的起源在哪</span></strong>，同時，山田宏指出，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>中國的新聞內容中不斷將疫情在世界蔓延因素，歸咎於日本與韓國應對情況差，他認為這樣的論調讓人不得不正視。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-03-03/373959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-03-03%2F373959&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVptiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=84a69c2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-03-03/373959</a>"},{"pid":"93b235b235786681d881004b9fff3e95129f7f37","tid":1908418,"uid":80724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:22:13.000Z","msg":"支那武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb0e8ad5395ac77b0b611d1151f35e885db0296","tid":1908418,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"Wuflu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fc7416a2111e47c9270b23f92067b2f2a0cbe5","tid":1908418,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎武漢肺炎武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b0f468945a2e8889fc12e432bb08c996a53397","tid":1908418,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:41:14.000Z","msg":"中國的新聞內容中不斷將疫情在世界蔓延因素，歸咎於日本與韓國應對情況差，他認為這樣的論調讓人不得不正視。<br />\n<br />\n先撩者賤<br />\n睇清楚中國人係幾卑鄙幾賤格幾低劣嘅人種<br />\n<br />\n自己地方爆發病毒<br />\n仲周圍話人應對唔好，想轉移視線<br />\n而家全世界更加要堅持叫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「<span style=\"color: green;\">武漢肺炎</span>」</span>"},{"pid":"244b936046e9d757ee74c279bbe67391220daf68","tid":1908418,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:41:25.000Z","msg":"叫中國肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecb5c347b65d970b1272508985b77b12381072d","tid":1908418,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"洗完名仲想話係人地先係起源地 痴撚線"},{"pid":"ac02002ea7e405cd9cfa62d37f59e2eaf12a8767","tid":1908418,"uid":186997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cV9jcCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcV9jcCU.jpg&h=f79f49bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfcb56d43d12df6ed2c41c8bdbfa37a56646a963","tid":1908418,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:49:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">武漢肺炎</span><br />\n順便正名非典先：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">廣州肺炎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d244efd9f3c5a07131a7037b16f849cbd9b78dad","tid":1908418,"uid":254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyT